            answer: { value: 7, unit: '' },
            solution: `Termerna $+y$ och $-y$ tar ut varandra vid ledvis addition:

$$ (x + y) + (x - y) = 11 + 3 $$

$$ 2x = 14 \\iff x = 7 $$

**Svar:** $x = 7$`,
